    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《杀青：序章》是一款中式梦核恐怖悬疑解谜游戏，玩家将扮演游戏主人公，在“雾山镇”展开一场梦幻和恐怖的冒险。 在这个熟悉又陌生的地方，主人公是否能逃出生天，了解灵异事件的真相？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >序章版本包含前两章游戏内容，玩家可以从序章了解到游戏的核心玩法、故事背景和前期的剧情内容。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3229180/extras/fcbaea7d57937ee3af158e227efd9895.avif?t=1733604459\" width=600 height=336 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏的故事背景发生在21世纪初的雾山镇，林清纱收录到了一部恐怖电影的邀约，但在前往片场的路上，发生了许多灵异事件，这到底是现实还是梦境？或许今晚要杀青的，可能不仅仅是电影。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3229180/extras/8de69b32617b3b2504b0964631acd0bf.avif?t=1733604459\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家将在雾山镇的医院，殡仪馆等场景展开一场梦核冒险，场景的设计、氛围都还原了世纪之初的熟悉感，让玩家在游戏过程中体验一个精彩的本土梦核故事。天马行空的美术场景，诡异的环境氛围，让玩家尽情体验深入骨髓的诡异感觉。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3229180/extras/0747b90996ab11eaa3b921905e5af293.avif?t=1733604459\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3229180/extras_big/0747b90996ab11eaa3b921905e5af293.avif?t=1733604459 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与林清纱、曲辉共同冒险，感受他们炙热的感情和羁绊，让游玩过程中有更强的代入感。通过探索场景的细节，找到事与物之间的关联，解开冒险中遇到的谜题，找出事件的真相，让梦魇结束。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3229180/extras/d2f3b09ebc4e74352d4f6239ecdfebfa.avif?t=1733604459\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3229180/extras_big/d2f3b09ebc4e74352d4f6239ecdfebfa.avif?t=1733604459 width=800 height=450 /></span></p>",
